text: Walter Coles (born 11 February 1928) is an English cricketer. He played two first-class matches for Cambridge University Cricket Club in 1949. ==See also== * List of Cambridge University Cricket Club players ==References== ==External links== * Category:1928 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Cambridge University cricketers Category:People from Northwood, London
